headline: Regions Bank Announces Winner of Company's Highest Honor for Community Involvement
summary: SHREVEPORT, La. - Regions Bankon Monday announced Digital Experience Researcher Kay Goke from the company's technology division has been honored with the 2025 Lee Ann Petty Heart of Service Award....
